name: Bolu Love
greetingText: I know i can be annoying knuckle headed stupid buh i just want to let you know that you mean so much to me!!
wishText: I hope your Birthday will always be as beautiful and full of love as you are. You deserve only the best, and I will always wish that for you Happy Birthday Adeboye Dorcas Boluwatife 🎈🎈🎈🎈🎈🎈🎈! ;)
